item.title: Blessed be the Name of the Lord, Most High!
item.description: Blessed be the name of the Lord, Blessed be the name of the Lord, Blessed be the name of the Lord, Most High! (Repeat) The Name of the Lord is a strong tower, The righteous run into it, And they are saved (repeat) Glory to the name of the Lord… Holy is the name of the Lord …
